⍝ ReplicateAxis.tc
⍝ ════════════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: LO integer scalar/vector; X∊⍳⍴⍴B; implicit ⎕IO
      ⍝ inv: (⍴Z)[X] ←→ +/|LO   (new axis length = sum of |LO|)
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ ⍴⍴B
      B ← ⎕RVAL 2 (4 5) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      LO ← 1+2∣|⎕RVAL 1 (,4) (,0 1 0 0 0)    ⍝ replicate along axis 1
      Z ← LO/[1]B
      ((⍴Z)[1]) ≡ +/|LO
1
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ ⍴⍴B
1
